@base = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@sellerToken = PASTE_TOKEN_SELLER
@driverToken = PASTE_TOKEN_DRIVER
@adminToken = PASTE_TOKEN_ADMIN

### Seller: lihat order masuk
GET {{base}}/seller/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{sellerToken}}

### Seller: proses order (Sedang Dikemas -> Menunggu Pengirim, buka job untuk driver)
POST {{base}}/seller/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID/process
Authorization: Bearer {{sellerToken}}

### Driver: cari job tersedia
GET {{base}}/driver/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

### Driver: ambil job
POST {{base}}/driver/jobs/PASTE_JOB_ID/take
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

### Driver: konfirmasi selesai
POST {{base}}/driver/jobs/PASTE_JOB_ID/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

### Admin: dashboard monitoring
GET {{base}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin: simulasi hari berikutnya (trigger overdue auto refund/return)
POST {{base}}/admin/simulate-next-day
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "days": 4 }
